<div id="search-box">

  <div class="content">
    <h1 class="home-tagline">Hack your next stay...</h1>
    <h2 class="home-subheader">Search and book listings in your destination of choice</h2>

    <form class="form-search" action="/search" method="GET">
      <div class="input-group">
        <input type="text" name='query' class='form-control' id='searchinput input-large search-query' placeholder='Enter a neighborhood in San Francisco...'>
        <span class="input-group-btn">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Search</button>
        </span>
      </div>
    </form>

  </div>
</div>
 

<div class="container">
  <div class="neighborhoods">
      <% @hoods.each do |hood, pic| %>
      
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
          <div class="thumbnails">
            <%= image_tag(pic, size: "328x250") %>
            <div class="caption">
              <h3><%= hood %></h3>
              <p><a href="#" class="btn btn-info" role="button">Book Tour</a> <a href="#" class="btn btn-default" role="button">Details</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="hacker-friends">
</div>

<div class="community">
  <div class="content">
    <h2 class="title">What's so special about co-living?</h1>
    <div class="content-row">
      <div class="content-text pull-left">
        <h3>SYNERGY</h3>
        <p class="blurb">Whether you're a free spirit looking to connect with other like-minded souls or a tech entrepreneur looking to meet other innovators and disruptors, community living is an excellent way to combine your efforts with others in an incredible way.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-icon pull-right">
        <%= image_tag("synergy.png", size: "120x120") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-row">
      <div class="content-icon pull-left">
         <%= image_tag("friend4.png", size: "120x120") %>
      </div>
      <div class="content-text pull-right">
        <h3>FRIENDS</h3>
        <p class="blurb">Living in a big city always has its social challenges.  Imagine having 10-20 instant friends to hang out with and an effortless social life as soon as you move in! Humans are incredibly social creatures built to live in groups.  Explore your social potential in one of our incredible communities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-row">
      <div class="content-text pull-left">
        <h3>AFFORDABLE HOUSING</h3>
        <p class="blurb">Stop burning money! We all know how UN-affordable San Francisco can be.  Save your money for awesome experiences and other things you need rather than spending your whole paycheck on housing!  Affordable living in San Francisco has never been this easy...</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-icon pull-right">
        <%= image_tag("moneyburning.png", size: "120x120") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="house-dinner">
</div>

<div class="quote-section">
  <div class="quote-content">
    <h3 class="quote">“If you want to go quickly, go alone. If you want to go far, go together.”</h3>
  </div>
</div>

